## ⚠ Sensor Fault Behaviour

The Receiver ECU continuously monitors the health of each sensor node.

If a sensor becomes unavailable or returns invalid data:

- Telemetry transmission continues uninterrupted.
- Remaining sensor values continue updating.
- A fault status is embedded in the telemetry frame.
- The dashboard immediately highlights the faulty sensor.
- System communication remains stable.

The image below demonstrates a **DS18B20 Sensor Fault**, while all other ECUs continue operating normally.

